# Keep non-served source out of the deployment.
#
# outputDirectory:"." (see vercel.json) would otherwise serve the entire repo
# root, which undercuts the point of the minify build (don't ship readable
# source). Ignore only files needed neither for the build nor for serving.
#
# IMPORTANT: do NOT ignore build-trainer.mjs — the deploy buildCommand runs it.

# Offline data-generation helpers (synthetic-data / teaching logic)
*.py

# Internal docs and notes
*.md

# Local env + build artifacts
.env*
trainer.min.html
clerk-auth.min.js
node_modules
